## How to use the python notebooks

First use the deep model comparison file for a clear understanding of why the final model was choosen. Feel free to add and compare your own models to this notebook.

Then run the model for prognosis file to train and optimise the *random forest regressor(RFR)* according the datasets. Again feel free to add in your own datasets. 

Finally, in the model integration file, refrence the model for prognosis and use it to make a battery health predition. Post this result to things speak clould or any other Iot cloud infrastructure, to get alerts. 
